// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lflczN 3 grounded spheres tangent plane, 2024 by jt

// Calculate tangent plane to three spheres placed on the plane z = 0
// Method: reflect ground plane at plane through sphere centers.

// tags: sphere, plane, three, tangent, triple

